channel.title: Getting this online
channel.description:
So I just recently started up an old Rsps server and I wanted to put it online. Knowing that I didn't have to change any of the IP's because they were already set to my no-ip form before. I did portforward my router and I checked to make sure it's open and all and it is but for some reason when I start up my server the port closes. I went onto the online status checker for the server and when I just have the DUC program running without the server online it says its online and playable but when I start uo the server it says it is offline. I don't know what to change or what do to since I thought it would work since everything is the same as before.
Help is much appreciated, Thanks
